The paper discusses distributed systems comprising mobile agents, which is a topic commonly studied in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also deals with problems related to consensus, clustering, gathering, and aggregation, which are topics studied in the subfields of distributed computing (cs.DC), distributed systems (cs.DS), control systems (cs.SY), and robotics (cs.RO). Hence, these subcategories are also likely to be relevant.
